{"tid":531690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場玩航拍　司機罰款","createTime":"2018-01-17T05:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T05:58:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"960216061e4b1aec28647d7c89f2de2ce535edd2","tid":531690,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180117/20276683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F20276683&d=W5fWDhjqhJPaoiRY8dxCEC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=9a050ac2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F20276683&h=b8e0c129\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180117/20276683</a><br />\n<br />\n機場玩航拍　司機罰款<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180117/large/a0804a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180117%2Flarge%2Fa0804a.gif&h=1b86bd12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告楊潤偉在機場禁區用航拍機玩自拍惹上官非。<br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年7月有港人候機往日本遊玩前，在機場禁區以手機操控迷你無人機，從高位自拍三張照片，並將相片上載至facebook及fb航拍討論區。機管局職員翌日從網上新聞得悉事件報警，港人回港時被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「開心幫自己影張相」<br />\n<br />\n報稱職業司機的被告楊潤偉（52歲）昨在東區法院承認違反《1995年飛航（香港）令》，求情稱無意影響他人，純粹「開心幫自己影張相」。裁判官考慮他一時貪玩，不熟悉有關法例，判罰款2,000元了事。<br />\n<br />\n楊承認於去年7月13日，在機場1號客運大樓離境中場客運廊（禁區）6樓近205號閘口，操作航空器而危害任何人或財產安全，同月17日被捕。涉案迷你無人機附相機可拍照，重量僅199克，飛行高度則有50米，民航處專家指屬法例規管的飛行器，其飛行時速可達28公里，一旦失控會危及途人安全及破壞閉路電視。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC279/18<br />\n■記者羅日昇、梁偉強"},{"pid":"a8a48a2128968ea0ce95b26bc5b344b473a35896","tid":531690,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:45:26.000Z","msg":"用支那野抵死"},{"pid":"d225ad0eb2c905fde2d244b8feaabe2a4aba9a10","tid":531690,"uid":29201,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"個樣打格又有張大頭照咩玩法"},{"pid":"86a95352e6a4bf80b5dbc89e229ba30bcbee70cf","tid":531690,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"幾大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}